title: Luxury Condo with Bay Views in St. Petersburg
description:
Experience luxury living in this stunning 12th-floor condo with panoramic views of Tampa Bay. This modern residence features floor-to-ceiling windows, an open concept layout, and high-end finishes throughout. The chef's kitchen boasts European cabinetry, quartz countertops, and top-of-the-line appliances.


The master suite offers a private balcony with breathtaking sunset views, while the spa-inspired bathroom includes a soaking tub and frameless glass shower. Building amenities include a resort-style pool, fitness center, concierge service, and secure parking. Located in the heart of downtown St. Pete, you're steps away from world-class dining, museums, and waterfront parks.

title: Stunning Waterfront Estate in Clearwater
description:
Welcome to this magnificent waterfront estate featuring breathtaking views of the Gulf of Mexico. This modern home boasts an open floor plan with high-end finishes throughout. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large island perfect for entertaining.

The spacious master suite includes a spa-like bathroom with dual vanities, soaking tub, and walk-in shower. Step outside to your private oasis with a heated pool, covered lanai, and direct water access. This home is perfect for those seeking the ultimate Florida lifestyle.

title: Charming Bungalow in Historic Dunedin
description:
Discover the charm of this beautifully renovated bungalow in the heart of historic Dunedin. This home perfectly blends vintage character with modern updates. The bright and airy living spaces feature original hardwood floors, updated fixtures, and fresh paint throughout.

The updated kitchen includes new cabinetry, quartz countertops, and modern appliances. Both bathrooms have been tastefully remodeled. The large fenced backyard is perfect for gardening or entertaining. Walk to downtown Dunedin's shops, restaurants, and the famous Pinellas Trail!
